6 Subject: Domestic relations; Domestic Violence Fatality Review Commission
7 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to expand the
8 scope of the Commission’s review to include near-fatal instances of domestic
9 violence; add new members to the Commission; and direct the persons who
10 have appointing authority to consider diversity when appointing members to
