12 An act relating to the Domestic Violence Fatality Review Commission
13 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
14 Sec. 1. 15 V.S.A. § 1140 is amended to read:
15 § 1140. DOMESTIC VIOLENCE FATALITY REVIEW COMMISSION
16 (a) The Domestic Violence Fatality Review Commission is established
17 within the Office of the Attorney General, in consultation with the Council on
18 Domestic Violence, for the following purposes:

